s.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(42,1,'2015-01-05 16:50:55','2015-01-05 16:50:55','[section class=\"text-left\"]\r\n[dropcap]Born on opposite sides of the country; we met and fell in love in Long Beach, we were engaged in Ohio, then married in SanFranciscos Golden Gate Park.  Weve catered LA to The Bay and this is our California culinary adventure! After year one in business, our daughter was born  and inspired the us to create the Baby Bun as a more economical slider version of everyones favorite sandwiches.[/dropcap][line class=\"transparent\"]\r\n[column large=\"6\" first=\"true\"]\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-2155 img-responsive\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/hg-restaurant2.jpg\" alt=\"jqg_13539536932\" width=\"640\" height=\"225\" />\r\n[/column]\r\n\r\n[column large=\"6\" last=\"true\"][panel title=\"Our Adventure\"]\r\nBorn on opposite sides of the country; we met and fell in love in Long Beach, we were engaged in Ohio, then married in SanFrancisco\'s Golden Gate Park.  We\'ve catered LA to The Bay and this is our California culinary adventure! After year one in business, our daughter was born  and inspired the us to create the \"Baby Bun\" as a more economical \"slider\" version of everyone\'s favorite sandwiches.\r\n[/panel][/column][line class=\"transparent\"]\r\n\r\n[column large=\"6\" first=\"true\"][panel title=\"The Bistro Bus Story\"]\r\nWhile looking for restaurant space closer to our family in the valley; we were blessed to find a classic 1975 taco truck just waiting to match up with our vintage concept of quality.  This is a  perfect way for us to spread local produce and the slow food movement to many valley communities. \r\n[/panel][/column][column large=\"6\" last=\"true\"]<img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-2155 img-responsive\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/hg-restaurant.jpg\" alt=\"jqg_13539536932\" width=\"640\" height=\"225\" />\r\n[/column][/section]\r\n\r\n[section style=\"alter\"]\r\n[column large=\"4\" first=\"true\"][panel title=\"Tina Mae\" image=\"48\" size=\"sm\" class=\"text-center\"]\r\nDone with passion... from the setting of the mise-en-place to the sensuous uncorking of the finest wine.\r\n[/panel][/column][column large=\"4\"][panel title=\"Shawn Carter\" image=\"50\" size=\"sm\" class=\"text-center\"]\r\nYou can be sure that when you order beef it is pure beef, GUARANTEED. All our beef is aged on our premises.\r\n[/panel][/column][column large=\"4\" last=\"true\"][panel title=\"Mia Wallace\" image=\"49\" size=\"sm\" class=\"text-center\"]\r\nIconic steak, should be two fingers thick, served on the bone and adorned with no more than a pinch of sea salt.\r\n[/panel][/column]\r\n[/section]','Our Story','Serving Highgrove Since 1987.','publish','open','open','','our-story','','','2015-02-04 00:57:04','2015-02-04 00:57:04','',0,'http://www.livelygreen.com/themes/highgrove/data/?page_id=42',0,'page','',0),(43,1,'2015-01-05 16:50:37','2015-01-05 16:50:37','','bg-app','','inherit','open','open','','bg-app','','','2015-01-05 16:50:37','2015-01-05 16:50:37','',42,'http://localhost:8080/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/bg-app.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(45,1,'2015-01-05 16:52:07','2015-01-05 16:52:07','','hg-restaurant','','inherit','open','open','','hg-restaurant','','','2015-01-05 16:52:07','2015-01-05 16:52:07','',0,'http://localhost:8080/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/hg-restaurant.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(46,1,'2015-01-05 16:52:16','2015-01-05 16:52:16','','hg-restaurant2','','inherit','open','open','','hg-restaurant2','','','2015-01-05 16:52:16','2015-01-05 16:52:16','',0,'http://localhost:8080/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/hg-restaurant2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(48,1,'2015-01-05 16:54:24','2015-01-05 16:54:24','','team1','','inherit','open','open','','team1','','','2015-01-05 16:54:24','2015-01-05 16:54:24','',0,'http://localhost:8080/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/team1.jpg',0,'attachment','